{"tid":1868818,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果黃店變埋街市","createTime":"2020-02-07T19:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T01:47:10.000Z","uid":331113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd30c2963f3536bd9cfb65e7cd66be8bbf4bea6","tid":1868818,"uid":331113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:51:47.000Z","msg":"小弟有個想法想同大家分享下，如果同意嘅話可以一齊呼籲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黃店</span></span>實行。<br />\n<br />\n要壯大<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黃色經濟圈</span></span>，就必須將佢所涵蓋嘅範圍擴大，咁樣就可以令其效果更為顯著。<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n<br />\n首先，要令黃店變堆超級市場/街市。黃店本身自己就要訂購野食，咁即係代表佢其實可以做堆分銷商依個部份，我地可以透過出示香港身分證同留低聯絡方法黎同佢一齊訂貨，咁樣就可以買餸都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黃色經濟圈</span></span>啦。<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n<br />\n&middot;拓展黃色經濟圈嘅業務<br />\n<br />\n&middot;支持黃色小店（誠哥咁有錢，都唔驚畀人搶生意㗎啦）<br />\n<br />\n&middot;買餸都可以畀 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真&bull;香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n&middot;依家啲野食畀<span style=\"color: blue;\">失智嘅人</span>搶哂，乜九都買唔都到，如果黃店可以咁做就可以提供到穩定嘅食物畀我地<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩錯，麻煩屌細力啲。<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港!"},{"pid":"0344578cf60994cbc23751ec3851493d92c89878","tid":1868818,"uid":331113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:57:14.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5258481fe912d304eae20fd316fd95a2262131e","tid":1868818,"uid":331113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:58:11.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488ff60a3ae32cf36a641c10b011564e473f1de0","tid":1868818,"uid":331113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:58:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" 